thread.title: Wall Street rebounds but China trade war fears linger

title: Wall Street rebounds but China trade war fears linger
text:
Wall Street rebounds but China trade war fears linger 3:50pm EDT - 01:49 
China hit back quickly against the Trump administration’s plans to impose tariffs on $50 billion in Chinese goods with a $50 billion list of its own - but a late-day stock market rally erased an early market plunge.
